snippet.title: We Suspect Foul Play - Release Trailer
snippet.description:
2 horrible crimes happened! Famous actress in Hollywood has been killed and Case of The Golden Idol mechanics have been stolen.

Play "We Suspect Foul Play" now on itch and solve these crimes: https://branegames.itch.io/we-suspect-foul-play

Game by:
Lorenzo Boni
BRANE

Trailer Music:
Franz Liszt - Totentanz performed by Neal O'Doan released under CC BY-SA 3.0 DEED license
